name: DEEP ROYAL "OSHEY UNLTD" TEE
description:
Look street fabulous in our snazzy fashion T-shirts.
The soft and rubbery textured print has got Big Dawg; our cheeky eye-patched friend flaunting his chunky munchy.

Choose an "OSHEY UNLTD" design colour from the drop down menu; printed on this fitted Deep Royal T-shirt.

Print size: A3
________________________________
INFO:
O.S.F.A: {Chest-53 cm/Length-70 cm}.
180g, 100%  ring-spun cotton.
Wash at 40° with similar colours. 
Hang to dry. 
Do not tumble dry or dry clean.

(www.facebook.com/urbankulcha)
